Anna Keaveney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anna_Keaveney 0 Anna Keaveney (born 5 October 1949, Runcorn, Cheshire, England – 20 November 2004) was an English actress best known for her role as Marie Jackson in the Channel 4 soap opera Brookside..She also appeared in an episode of Birds of a Feather as Green party member of parliament candidate. She appeared in the films Shirley Valentine, The 51st State, and in several other TV series including Ali G Indahouse, Emmerdale, Footballer's Wives, and Peak Practice. Anna made her final film appearance as Nellie in Vera Drake (2004).
